import {
    Link
} from "react-router-dom";
import "./Navbar.module.css"
import Dropdown from 'react-multilevel-dropdown'

function Navbar() {
    return (
        <Dropdown
            title='Dropdown title'
        >
            <Dropdown.Item
            >
                Item 1
            </Dropdown.Item>
            <Dropdown.Item>
                Item 2
                <Dropdown.Submenu>
                    <Dropdown.Item>
                        Subitem 1
                    </Dropdown.Item>
                </Dropdown.Submenu>
            </Dropdown.Item>
        </Dropdown>
    )
}

export default Navbar
